---
const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
---
<footer class="bg-brand-primary text-brand-light py-16 md:py-24 mt-auto">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-8 md:px-12 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-12 md:gap-8">
    
    <!-- Brand -->
    <div class="md:col-span-5 flex flex-col items-center md:items-start text-center md:text-left space-y-6">
      <h3 class="text-3xl font-serif font-semibold tracking-wide">
        Melisa <span class="italic font-light">Carpintero</span>
      </h3>
      <p class="text-brand-light/70 text-base max-w-sm leading-relaxed">
        Especialista en bienestar infantil y desarrollo emocional. Brindando un espacio seguro y acogedor para el crecimiento de los más pequeños en Panamá.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Quick Links -->
    <div class="md:col-span-3 flex flex-col items-center md:items-start text-center md:text-left space-y-6">
      <h4 class="font-sans text-xs tracking-[0.25em] uppercase text-brand-accent font-bold">Enlaces</h4>
      <ul class="space-y-4">
        <li><a href="/" class="text-brand-light/80 hover:text-brand-accent hover:translate-x-1 block transition-all text-sm">Inicio</a></li>
        <li><a href="/#sobre-mi" class="text-brand-light/80 hover:text-brand-accent hover:translate-x-1 block transition-all text-sm">Sobre Mí</a></li>
        <li><a href="/#especialidades" class="text-brand-light/80 hover:text-brand-accent hover:translate-x-1 block transition-all text-sm">Especialidades</a></li>
        <li><a href="/pago" class="text-brand-light/80 hover:text-brand-accent hover:translate-x-1 block transition-all text-sm">Agendar Cita / Tarifas</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- Contact Info -->
    <div class="md:col-span-4 flex flex-col items-center md:items-start text-center md:text-left space-y-6">
      <h4 class="font-sans text-xs tracking-[0.25em] uppercase text-brand-accent font-bold">Contacto</h4>
      <div class="space-y-3">
        <p class="text-brand-light/80 text-sm flex items-center justify-center md:justify-start gap-2">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="w-4 h-4 text-brand-accent">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15 10.5a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" />
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19.5 10.5c0 7.142-7.5 11.25-7.5 11.25S4.5 17.642 4.5 10.5a7.5 7.5 0 1115 0z" />
          </svg>
          Ciudad de Panamá, Panamá
        </p>
        <p class="text-brand-light/80 text-sm flex items-center justify-center md:justify-start gap-2">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="w-4 h-4 text-brand-accent">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12.75L11.25 15 15 9.75M21 12c0 1.268-.63 2.39-1.593 3.068a3.745 3.745 0 01-1.043 3.296 3.745 3.745 0 01-3.296 1.043A3.745 3.745 0 0112 21c-1.268 0-2.39-.63-3.068-1.593a3.746 3.746 0 01-3.296-1.043 3.745 3.745 0 01-1.043-3.296A3.745 3.745 0 013 12c0-1.268.63-2.39 1.593-3.068a3.745 3.745 0 011.043-3.296 3.746 3.746 0 013.296-1.043A3.746 3.746 0 0112 3c1.268 0 2.39.63 3.068 1.593a3.746 3.746 0 013.296 1.043 3.746 3.746 0 011.043 3.296A3.745 3.745 0 0121 12z" />
          </svg>
          Atención Presencial y Virtual
        </p>
      </div>
      <a href="/pago" class="mt-4 inline-block pb-1 border-b border-brand-accent text-brand-light hover:text-white hover:border-white transition-colors text-sm font-medium">
        Reserva tu sesión ahora →
      </a>
    </div>

  </div>

  <div class="container mx-auto px-8 md:px-12 mt-16 pt-8 border-t border-brand-light/10 flex flex-col items-center">
    <p class="text-brand-light/40 text-xs text-center">
      &copy; {currentYear} Lic. Melisa Carpintero. Todos los derechos reservados.
    </p>
  </div>
</footer>
